<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg shadow">
  <div class="px-6 py-4">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-1">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">How to Verify Social Media Accounts</h3>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">‚úì Verification Checklist:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold mt-0.5">1.</span>
                <span><strong>Open the account link</strong> - Click the URL to view the actual account</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold mt-0.5">2.</span>
                <span><strong>Confirm identity</strong> - Verify it's the correct person (check name, photo, bio)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold mt-0.5">3.</span>
                <span><strong>Check account type</strong> - Verify it belongs in the correct category (Campaign, Official Office, or Personal)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold mt-0.5">4.</span>
                <span><strong>Verify URL format</strong> - Ensure URL is clean (no tracking parameters after ? or &)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold mt-0.5">5.</span>
                <span><strong>Cross-check</strong> - Use Google search "[Name] [Platform] [State]" to confirm</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="grid gap-3 text-sm">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-3 border border-green-100">
              <h5 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1.5 flex items-center gap-1">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                If Account is Correct:
              </h5>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Click the checkmark icon (‚úì) to verify as accurate</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-3 border border-purple-100">
              <h5 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1.5">‚úèÔ∏è If Account Needs Editing:</h5>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-1.5">Click <span class="text-purple-600 font-medium">Edit</span>, update the URL, then click <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-purple-600 text-white rounded text-xs font-medium">Save</span></p>
              <p class="text-purple-700 text-xs"><strong>Note:</strong> Editing an account will mark it for secondary verification to ensure accuracy.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-3 border border-gray-200">
              <h5 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1.5">‚ö†Ô∏è If Account Doesn't Exist:</h5>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-1.5">Click <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 rounded text-xs font-medium">Mark Not Found</span>, then click the checkmark (‚úì) to verify the platform has no account</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs"><strong>Tip:</strong> If you previously entered a URL by mistake, it will be saved in case you need to restore it.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-3 border border-orange-100">
              <h5 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1.5">üîÑ To Unverify an Account:</h5>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Click the slash-through circle icon (‚äò) to unverify, then you can edit it</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-3">
            <div class="flex gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <div class="text-sm text-amber-900">
                <strong>Account Types:</strong>
                <ul class="mt-1 space-y-1 text-amber-800">
                  <li><strong>Campaign:</strong> Accounts used for election runs (e.g., "@SmithForSenate")</li>
                  <li><strong>Official Office:</strong> Accounts for current officeholders (e.g., "@SenSmith")</li>
                  <li><strong>Personal:</strong> Personal accounts not affiliated with campaigns or office</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-purple-50 border border-purple-200 rounded-lg p-3">
            <div class="flex gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <div class="text-sm text-purple-900">
                <strong>Secondary Verification:</strong>
                <span class="text-purple-800">When you modify an account's data (change URL or mark as not found), it will be flagged for secondary verification by another team member. This ensures data quality through a two-person verification process.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <% if local_assigns[:show_guide_link] != false %>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-end gap-3 pt-2">
              <a href="<%= researcher_guide_path %>#verification-methods" target="_blank" class="text-sm text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium flex items-center gap-1">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"/>
                </svg>
                Read Full Verification Guide
              </a>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
